{"tid":1556823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自612起 已有101單自殺個案","createTime":"2019-09-10T01:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:11:33.000Z","uid":144497,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"13e017eddae2db6763b67af43de73e28f6670838","tid":1556823,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10219797941159919&amp;id=1261125378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10219797941159919%26id%3D1261125378&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=678e7e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10219797941159919&amp;id=1261125378</a><br />\n<br />\n當你以為，係過去24小時內，只有6單自殺個案的時候...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實自612開始，香港累積已有101單自殺個案。</span><br />\n(謝謝網友 Dayi Yeung 提供資料，9月10日更正為102單自殺個案，因此修正左Excel表的相片。)<br />\n<br />\n而其中：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6月</span>份有<span style=\"color: orange;\">22宗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">7月</span>份有<span style=\"color: green;\">21宗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">8月</span>份卻有<span style=\"color: blue;\">35宗</span><br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">9月</span>份，截至9月9日為止，已有<span style=\"color: red;\">24宗</span>個案，已經超越<span style=\"color: orange;\">6月</span>及<span style=\"color: green;\">7月</span>份的個案數目。<br />\n而當中絕大多數都是墮樓個案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK1kgu4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK1kgu4.jpg&h=d8a39023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPN3YJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPN3YJt.jpg&h=81c75c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogUh3ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogUh3ab.jpg&h=e8aa027a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RonzkWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRonzkWV.jpg&h=cbcb289b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNYOqoD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNYOqoD.jpg&h=affd159b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你問，這當中是否隱含了甚麼模式，暗示某些恐怖的事情正在發生？<br />\n<br />\n又或者，是不是現在發生的都是十分正常，畢竟2017年全年總共也有916宗自殺個案，現在3個月總計都只是102單，是小巫見大巫？<br />\n<br />\n抱歉，我並不是一位專業的數據分析師，我最多能夠做的，就是花幾晚時間在網上紀錄低所有自殺個案的資料去製作以下的Excel表，但我不介意，如果閣下有意發揮一下分析的才能，需要用到這份Excel表，請PM我，我會將Excel表發給你一起研究。<br />\n<br />\n最後，看完之後，我會說：<br />\n<br />\n我全家都好幸福，對目前的生活非常滿意，感情狀態非常穩定，經濟上雖然有壓力但卻是我努力向上的動力。<br />\n我生性樂觀，喜歡挑戰，刻苦耐勞，心境平和喜悅，所以在任何時候，「放棄生命」也絕對不會是我的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，請多點關心身邊的人，確保「放棄生命」也絕對不會是他們的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位。"},{"pid":"0b46275442683dcecc44e02566ef6c6fbcf6b7f7","tid":1556823,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0cade538a585d1dddd617f9e44dc8ea113281992","tid":1556823,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e16ae70c621f55d3f994daa58cc21876df98dd3","tid":1556823,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6921ffe1849ad51b44fe183c0fcd655938b4698","tid":1556823,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-lin